data.title: Princeton Independent School District
data.text:
Welcome to the Princeton ISD Band. The Princeton band enrolls students from 6th through 12th grades who study with a dedicated teaching faculty as well as private lesson instructors.

Music is the the fundamental piece of the human experience. Music Education is therefore a necessary endeavor to ensure that the whole child is being educated. This includes skill development, cognitive understanding, and aesthetic appreciation for many forms of music.
